JSON mode NEVER applies themes or colors. JSONPresenter output is always structured JSON data — no ANSI escape codes, no theme lookup, no color of any kind. This is non-negotiable: JSON output must be parseable by any JSON consumer without stripping escape codes. --json overrides --color=always, the user's theme preference, and every other color-related setting. See <ref spec="output.flag_precedence">flag precedence</ref> and <ref spec="output.json_mode">JSON mode</ref>.